to these reactivated bodies.

506
01:18:26,782 --> 01:18:28,825
Don't shoot!

507
01:18:39,252 --> 01:18:41,171
Johnnie...

508
01:18:49,346 --> 01:18:53,016
Jesus god-damn holy reverent shit!

509
01:18:53,141 --> 01:18:58,480
What in the name of Jupiter's balls
are you doing out here alone, lady?

510
01:20:18,101 --> 01:20:23,523
- Tell me, chief, are they slow-moving?
- Yeah, they're all messed up.

511
01:20:42,500 --> 01:20:44,961
Shoot the fuck down!

512
01:20:47,213 --> 01:20:50,425
They're us.
We're them, and they're us.

513
01:20:51,968 --> 01:20:53,678
Say what?

514
01:20:56,264 --> 01:20:58,308
Nothing.

515
01:21:01,061 --> 01:21:04,731
- Having fun?
- Give me a break.

516
01:22:54,090 --> 01:22:55,758
Drag that out of here.

517
01:22:55,883 --> 01:23:00,305
I'm going in. Watch your back.
There may be more of them.

518
01:23:12,900 --> 01:23:15,862
You came back.

519
